 Syntax:  When you want to challenge a user  :  .fight <user>
          When you want to accept a challenge:  .fight yes
          When you want to wimp out          :  .fight no
          When you want to reset the fight   :  .fight reset
          To see the current fight challenged:  .fight

Results:  The fight command allows two users to fight to the "death"
          on a talker.  The odds vary depending on who you fight.  If
          you choose someone with a higher rank...you have less chance 
          of winning.  Your odds of winning are.. 
             user rank 1 odds : user rank 2 odds.
          See .ranks for those numbers.
